data.description: Beautiful corner lot home! Start making great memories in this four bedrooms, two bathrooms home! Bright and cozy living room lead you towards your new kitchen, perfectly complemented by granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Check out that charming fireplace! Very good size bedrooms. Walk-in closet and garden tub in the master bathroom. Wonderful Jack-and-Jill secondary bathroom. Low maintenance backyard, kids playground, and storage. See this home today!
